Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}could{\i0} it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Omelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like more coffee, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Papa said he'd rather have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, it's amazing you knew that, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Yuu, you're it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always us! No fair, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it's fair. It's rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're a rock-paper-scissors champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you challenge me,\Nthe Queen of Rock-Paper-Scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're all saying what you're going to throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Mama! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa bought it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very cute, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're a big girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't call me "shorty!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do any of you have a boy you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys are so immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya, don't you like Kousuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mai, you like Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru likes Kousuke, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya, you like Kousuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like any boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru has liked him since kindergarten. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't like Hajime...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He helped you up when you fell,\Nso that's why you like him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime likes you too, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like Mai at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Haruka! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not friends anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka is {\i1}vicious{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,everything she says is untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of her classmates have been hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've received numerous parental complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But, dear—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't raising a child the mother's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an early start tomorrow. I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, am I sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They all say I'm creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, when are you coming home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk about Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that Haruka is your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I don't think I'm going to make it home from work tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear? Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Something evil has possessed my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, can't you exorcise it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a simple priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it only my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa will come home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Whose fault do you think this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, lately Mama's been drinking a lot and getting mad so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And Papa won't even come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Papa, and my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they all hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll stay with us all day today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go out this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something to do as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, you're going to a hotel with Akiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mama, you're going to dinner with Mister Yoshino! No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know any woman by that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you? Who the hell is this man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You have to believe me, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just making stuff up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Again? You're doing it again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're horrible, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying so hard to ruin our lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're abandoning her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do about Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I give a damn about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll never do anything to make you mad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even do the cooking and cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Mama, please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go! Don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you had never been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Kumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...rry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters aren't welcome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna read your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why your parents abandoned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,250)}Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(80,250)}Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(80,250)}Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(80,250)}Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I'm not. I'm not a—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(80,0)}Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretended to be our friend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,just so you could break into our minds and laugh at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! We're best friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all alone too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was {\i1}you{\i0} feeding that cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it to a shelter, so don't let me see you around here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're transferring?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck at your new school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally we're rid of this headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kotoura Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kotoura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one's going to be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that? What a freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poor Manabe, having to sit next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same no matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,514)\i1}If only everyone were like this boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and just ignored me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd be content.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:57.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One morning I suddenly realized it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:02.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}I realized that I want to know more about you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:07.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}How weird that my heart thumps and I get nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}You only have to stand next to me and I might faint
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:17.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}And still you worm your way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}deeper into my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(100,100)\blur1}Love,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(575,1050)\fad(100,100)\blur1}love,
