Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kotoura, where did you move here from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that I really want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should never have become the class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to know, don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, which club are you going to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't join the tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm not interested in tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her? Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Moritani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. You remember my invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, to come to your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your house a karate dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shot down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She looked so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must really want my martial arts prowess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not after your "prowess," whether it exists or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you, so I just blurted that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did I say that out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! I'm so embarrassed!
