Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat together, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That looks so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if she'd give me a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa, it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Kotoura make this herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like everyone in class said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But keep the magic tricks to a minimum, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go overboard, you'll scare people off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and it'll be hard to make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business. And it's not magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the croquette is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't just take things without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mooornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Morninin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}One, two, three, four, five...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura! Be my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.59,Alt,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup! Hup! Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow. Ow. Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura! We should walk home together sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going this way too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you used to the school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hang around me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "why"? Of course I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why {\i1}do{\i0} I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, why {\i0}do{\i1} I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Hey, so tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the secret to that mind reading trick you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could read people's minds, I could do anything I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing cool about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "idiot"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, so I called you an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know {\i1}anything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you weren't in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It all starts with a kiss... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you thinking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}can{\i0} read people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it ESP?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is. You get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want me hearing your thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think about anything dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ESP's gonna be the end of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No man can endure the torment of controlling his lust!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}petrified!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna treat me like a total pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was {\i1}that{\i0} all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met such a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if it isn't Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want something perverted in return, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your confidence is less than overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, just hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these ingredients for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great you help out at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's green.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho-Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the driver's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply didn't care about the red light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must get it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just an intrusive, creepy, mind-reading mon—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your house near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There. That'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really {\i1}do{\i0} live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do your parents live?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole life, I've heard thoughts\Nwithout really understanding them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is make sure no one gets close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why at school, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to get close to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll only end up getting hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously want to be isolated?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to "hurt people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a load of bull! {\i1}You're{\i0} the one who's hurting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the only thing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't like being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't want to hurt or be hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing more horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,more utterly horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,than being abandoned by the people I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm better off just being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you can read minds or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,people who want to leave are going to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But not everyone is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's try this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You... {\alpha&HFF&}mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You... mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, as far as I'm concerned, we're already friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you totally are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the {\i1}heck{\i0} are you thinking about at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing a girl crying is kind of a turn-on, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You freak! Dirty lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling a lecher?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Betrayed by my own insatiable manliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to know you, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:22:04.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(525,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}How do you stand again when something trips you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:17.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,750)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Can truth be found by thinking about the days to come?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.06,0:22:26.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(775,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We all come into this world alone when we are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and precisely because of that,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.25,0:22:34.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we try to live life with others from then on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:42.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Back then you taught me the strength to live and the meaning to it all,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.63,0:22:48.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and I embrace it with all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:54.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}So that in all things around us the flower of hope may bloom,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.51,0:23:00.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:07.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,525)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kotoura? Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a ton of people on the other side of the TV thinking dirty thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura is only allowed to be the star of {\i1}my{\i0} fantasies!
